This workflow initiates on a scheduled basis, retrieves a watchlist from a spreadsheet, extracts product and pricing data, 
checks for substantial price reductions, and sends email alerts for watches with significant discounts. 
The process is fully automated and ensures timely notification of price drops to interested recipients.
Industry
Retail & E-commerce - Retail Analytics
Link: https://app.opus.com/app/workflow/share/496f922e-da25-49f5-90f2-739cb64a35bb
